title: AHS: 1984 Episode 5 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed! | "Red Dawn"
author: Think Story
comment: Row row row your boat, gently down with screams. ⛵🔪

Best 2 scenes: 
Brooke stabbing Montana in the leg & throwing the boom box at her. 
Xavier’s archery happy dance.
I like how ghost Ray has no pulse but still produced condensation on the oxygen mask from his breath.

"It's your fault, my future is in Radio" 
Xavier's dialogues in this episode were sarcastically funny.
These 5 episodes have been pretty perfect to me. Billie Lourd and Cody Fern are killing it, Leslie Grossman, too.
description:
